    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may create a darkness that is unnaturally edgy. Any creature inside the darkness must succeed at a Reflex save or take 1d6 slashing damage per 3 caster levels (minimum 1d6). Creatures who remain within this area of darkness must save at the end of your subsequent turns or take additional slashing damage. If a creature enters this area of darkness after it is created, they must immediately save or also suffer this damage. A creature may only be affected by Edge Of Night once per round, regardless of how many times they enter or exit the area that round.</p>\n",
